{"tid":2297451,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"正式宣布香港車手李英健同港共冇分別","createTime":"2020-11-23T09:41:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-23T15:08:01.000Z","uid":228945,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"1e025962a0b1897daa473b4feee033b8081f7566","tid":2297451,"uid":228945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T09:41:21.000Z","msg":"明明自己車隊同另一支中國車隊（第二、三行）<br />\n都犯同一條規例<br />\n但一齊聯手投訴頭車香港車手歐陽若曦<br />\n歐陽俾人罰30秒 自己就升排位<br />\n最後兩支車隊一齊上頒獎台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而家出post學人講體育精神<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1Qbzxzu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1Qbzxzu.png&h=76a11cc3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/X2a1czv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FX2a1czv.jpg&h=49b8e383&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nMarchy Lee 李英健<br />\n<br />\n而回顧今年的澳門GT盃賽事，在排位賽中明顯是有違規情況。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">根據賽例Article 3.4，在Rolling Start時，所有賽車必須在自己的「起跑格」（Starting Grid) 範圍內起步。而按Article 3.5的規定，每名車手必須確保其賽車與旁邊的賽車，保持不少了一架車的闊度距離。</span><br />\n<br />\n再花多一分鐘，看看歷年來澳門GT盃的起步圖片。對比起2018，2019的賽事，今年比賽起步時確有「異樣」，明顯越過了自己的「起跑格」，擠向了旁邊的車手。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">違反規則，理應接受處罰，而不是委過於人，為自己的失誤砌詞推搪。因為賽例上列出的不單是白紙黑字的規條，更加是保障車手們安全的生命線，不容半分妥協。這是所有專業運動員應有的態度，一位有30年經驗的職業車手，沒有理由不明白。</span><br />\n<br />\n互聯網年代，社交媒體盛行。每人都有權利在自己的平台上發表個人感受，尋求認同，也屬理解之內。但作為一個公眾人物，實在應該謹言慎行，黑白分明。<br />\n<br />\n賽事完滿結束，我亦希望當中一切爭議也能完結。作為職業運動員，繼續為體育界、賽車界找出疫情下的新出路。<br />\n<br />\n謝謝大家。<br />\n<br />\n李英健Marchy<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/666157286815546/posts/3446674872097093/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F666157286815546%2Fposts%2F3446674872097093%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=4eD5kuUGVNxCcHpGsLYUnXO0ZW31AiaZ%2BXmqixBX3cM%3D&h=3337e088\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/666157286815546/posts/3446674872097093/?d=n</a>"},{"pid":"d3e97254feddb128e709bdc2a638016aa049e107","tid":2297451,"uid":228945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T09:44:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e02e9f71dd70864ce23b1834044c59f3c777c008","tid":2297451,"uid":228945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T09:45:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25ed37be26354b6975692b052b4abb2193dc4c8f","tid":2297451,"uid":79410,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T09:52:31.000Z","msg":"可唔可以拆訴到佢取消冠亞軍?"},{"pid":"df83830fc9610d4d3cf92bb4b7f9edf299ae2d92","tid":2297451,"uid":228945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"25ed37be26354b6975692b052b4abb2193dc4c8f","tid":2297451,"uid":79410,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T09:52:31.000Z","msg":"可唔可以拆訴到佢取消冠亞軍?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T09:55:48.000Z","msg":"咁可能要上到fia層面"},{"pid":"c91b6a2003e3f39669a1e8d87c674218ddc0bf1b","tid":2297451,"uid":228945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T10:10:28.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"59ada651e2efe8d5bd5813a87de43855720517a8","tid":2297451,"uid":31834,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T10:20:57.000Z","msg":"呢條撚屌向內都係行內笑料 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c93601718732fd016d29cadee51fa11271079735","tid":2297451,"uid":228945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"59ada651e2efe8d5bd5813a87de43855720517a8","tid":2297451,"uid":31834,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T10:20:57.000Z","msg":"呢條撚屌向內都係行內笑料 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T10:33:04.000Z","msg":"有嘢爆？"},{"pid":"15ab1ab2e9b4c51de9aaf5273740a08f56abc260","tid":2297451,"uid":69873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"re